                            </p>
                           
                            <h4>Wimbledon 2021: Aryna Sabalenka reaches 3rd round after hard-fought win, Kaja Juvan knocks out Belinda Bencic</h4>
                            <p>
                                No.102 Kaja Juvan defeated No.9 seed Belinda Bencic 6-3, 6-3 in opening round while Aryna Sabalenka survived an early scare to sail into the second round at Wimbledon 2021.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Second seed Aryna Sabalenka dropped the opening set in her second-round match before powering to a 4-6, 6-3, 6-3 victory over Katie Boulter while 9th seed Belinda Bencic was knocked out after suffering a 3-6, 3-6 defeat in women's singles 1st-round to Kaja Juvan.
